OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Then staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with increasing clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Breezy at times,
OL,10,Fespecially in the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FDry, warm and bright or sunny
OL,13,Fthrough much of the day. Sunshine
OL,14,Fturning hazier in the afternoon as
OL,15,Fcloud spreads east. Chance of the odd
OL,16,Fspot of rain in evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
